cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.IR 

This paper deals with natural language processing and neural networks, which are commonly associated with the categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper involves information retrieval, as it aims to generate dictionary definitions for words, which could fall under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR).
